    %autoreload
import pandas as pd
import anndata as ad
from src.scrofit import SCRoFit

obj_dict = {}
for sample in ['Young1', 'Young2', 'Old1', 'Old2']:
    print('-----', sample)
    st_adata = ad.read_h5ad(f'../data/Aging_data/adata/{sample}_ST.adata')
    sm_adata = ad.read_h5ad(f'../data/Aging_data/adata/{sample}_SC_SM.adata')
    adata_dict = {'ST': st_adata, 'SM': sm_adata}

    obj = SCRoFit(adata_dict)
    obj.mapping(
            mapping_method='MCMF', alpha=1, beta=1, k=3,
            n_thread=6, n_batch=1000,
            verbose=False)    
    obj.check_slides(s=0.5)
    obj_dict[sample] = obj

    for sample in ['Young1', 'Young2', 'Old1', 'Old2']:
    obj = obj_dict[sample]
    sm_adata = obj.adata_dict['SM']
    st_adata = obj.adata_dict['ST']
    df = st_adata[sm_adata.obsm['mappingflow_MCMF'].nonzero()[1]].obs
    df = df[['Region', 'Region_2', 'Region_3', 'spotID', 'hires_x', 'hires_y', 'CellType']]
    df = df.reset_index()
    sm_df = sm_adata.obs[['run', 'pixel', 'x', 'y', 'align_x', 'align_y']]
    sm_df[['spatial_MCMF_map_x', 'spatial_MCMF_map_y']] = sm_adata.obsm['spatial_MCMF_map']
    sm_df = sm_df.reset_index()
    df = pd.concat([sm_df, df], axis=1)
    df.to_csv(f'../data/Aging_data/{sample}_SM_meta_SCRoFit.csv')
